                      "fill": "#111111",
                      "textGrowth": "fixed-width",
                      "width": "fill_container",
                      "content": "\"This award recognises the unsung heroes of healthcare — the infection prevention teams working tirelessly to keep patients safe. Environmental hygiene is not just about cleanliness; it is the foundation of patient safety.\"",
